{"tid":2355638,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【8.6 深水埗】襲警罪成判囚 3 周　水上運動教練放棄上訴即時服刑","createTime":"2021-01-06T08:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T09:00:13.000Z","uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c8d13dfb9b633e652aa849640fc266dea9d3edc8","tid":2355638,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:33:51.000Z","msg":"2019 年 8 月大批示威者包圍深水埗警署，警方展開驅散行動，期間一名水上運動教練被指從後推跌一名警署警長，經審訊後裁定襲警罪成，判監禁 3 星期。他不服定罪向高院提上訴，案件排期今日（6 日）處理，<span class=\"red\">惟開庭時表示放棄上訴，需要即時服刑。</span><br />\n<br />\n裁判官梁嘉琪裁決時稱，被告稱擔心女友安全而跑去找她，繼而衝入警方防線。裁判官質疑為何不打電話，反問「跑步會快過打電話？」，又認為他以警長為目標，行為屬「偷襲」。裁判官續指警員證供可靠，被告證供不盡不實，裁定襲警罪成，拒絕辯方建議索取報告，終判被告監禁 3 星期。被告當時獲准以 2 萬元保釋等候上訴。"},{"pid":"30602a5f95454a4765dbc9d55b6eea3d5807f229","tid":2355638,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:34:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/8-6-%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97-%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-3-%E5%91%A8-%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E6%95%99%E7%B7%B4%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%9C%8D%E5%88%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F8-6-%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597-%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-3-%25E5%2591%25A8-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2595%2599%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%25A3%2584%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%2588%2591%2F&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImSuJrf%2BHou%2F%2F5XtIYOa%2FW4Y%3D&h=26c98614\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F8-6-%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597-%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-3-%25E5%2591%25A8-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2595%2599%25E7